@host = http://localhost:5076

### Which providers are active (Gemini vs local fallback)
GET {{host}}/api/blogs/info
Accept: application/json

### Browse all blogs (no embeddings)
GET {{host}}/api/blogs
Accept: application/json

### NORMAL search (SQL ILIKE) — "secure my APIs" returns nothing, no literal match
GET {{host}}/api/blogs/search/normal?q=secure my APIs
Accept: application/json

### VECTOR search — same query surfaces JWT / API Key Authentication blogs
GET {{host}}/api/blogs/search/vector?q=secure my APIs&take=5
Accept: application/json

### RAG — retrieve relevant blogs by vector search, then answer with the LLM
GET {{host}}/api/blogs/ask?q=How do I secure my APIs?&take=5
Accept: application/json
